patthana23.23:1.1_0: Nasaṅkiliṭṭhasaṅkilesikaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā asaṅkiliṭṭhasaṅkilesiko kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.23:2.1_0: Nasaṅkiliṭṭhasaṅkilesikaṁ naakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā saṅkiliṭṭhasaṅkilesiko akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.23:3.1_0: Nasaṅkiliṭṭhasaṅkilesikaṁ naabyākataṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca asaṅkiliṭṭhasaṅkilesiko abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
